text: Cleveland is a township of about 1,600 people in Le Val-Saint-François Regional County Municipality in the Estrie region of Quebec, Canada. It was named after George Nelson Cleveland, the first mayor. ==Demographics== ===Population=== ===Language=== Mother tongue (2011) {| class="wikitable" |- ! Language ! Population !
